Most probably you have enabled **Cross-site request forgery (CSRF)**. You need either provide `_csrf` parameter in the request or disable CSRF using Spring Security Configuration:

    @EnableWebSecurity
    public class WebSecurityConfig extends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter {

	    @Override
	    protected void configure(HttpSecurity http) throws Exception {
		    http
			    .csrf().disable();
	    }
    }

See [Spring Security documentation for CSRF][1] for more details.


  [1]: https://docs.spring.io/spring-security/site/docs/5.0.x/reference/html/csrf.html

